Arthur Lake (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arthur_Lake_(actor) 0 Arthur Lake (born Arthur Silverlake Jr., April 17, 1905 – January 9, 1987) was an American actor known best for bringing Dagwood Bumstead, the bumbling husband of Blondie, to life in film, radio and television.
